  <brief_title>Ferinject® Assessment in Patients With IRon Deficiency and Chronic Heart Failure (FAIR-HF)</brief_title>
  <acronym>FAIR-HF</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomised Double-blind Controlled Phase III Study to Compare the Efficacy and Safety of Intravenous Iron Carboxymaltose (Ferinject®) With Placebo in Patients With Chronic Heart Failure and Iron Deficiency</official_title>
