  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to evaluate the efficacy of Ferinject® in improving symptoms of CHF in
      patients with iron deficiency. Analyses will focus both on subjective and objective measures.
      Furthermore, the tolerability and safety of Ferinject® treatment will be evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
